We asked Brother James Dyson that question.

00:51:23.980 --> 00:51:26.980
As a young man, he was overconfident,

00:51:26.980 --> 00:51:28.980
but he reached a turning point.

00:51:28.980 --> 00:51:29.980
What was it?

00:51:29.980 --> 00:51:31.980
And where has it led him?

00:51:31.980 --> 00:51:34.980
Please listen to his intriguing story.

00:51:38.860 --> 00:51:41.860
I came from a rather large family.

00:51:41.860 --> 00:51:44.860
We went to church from our youth on.

00:51:44.860 --> 00:51:47.860
I guess I really stopped going to church

00:51:47.860 --> 00:51:49.860
when I was a teenager.

00:51:49.860 --> 00:51:53.860
I graduated from high school in 1965.

00:51:53.860 --> 00:51:57.860
Since the Vietnam War was raging,

00:51:57.860 --> 00:52:00.860
I knew I would have to make a decision.

00:52:00.860 --> 00:52:02.860
I didn't want to fight in Vietnam

00:52:02.860 --> 00:52:05.860
because I didn't want to get killed first of all.

00:52:05.860 --> 00:52:08.860
And I didn't really want to be put in a position

00:52:08.860 --> 00:52:10.860
where I might have to kill someone else.

00:52:10.860 --> 00:52:13.860
And so I decided that the best thing for me to do,

00:52:13.860 --> 00:52:16.860
instead of trying to dodge the draft,

00:52:16.860 --> 00:52:19.860
was to join a form of the military,

00:52:19.860 --> 00:52:21.860
where I wouldn't have to fight.

00:52:21.860 --> 00:52:23.860
I worked on airplanes.

00:52:23.860 --> 00:52:25.860
Every night was an adventure.

00:52:25.860 --> 00:52:27.860
You know, when you're off base,

00:52:27.860 --> 00:52:29.860
you're either downtown with the black market,

00:52:29.860 --> 00:52:32.860
the clubs, buying and selling drugs.

00:52:32.860 --> 00:52:34.860
It was just a wild scene.

00:52:34.860 --> 00:52:37.860
After my military service was over

00:52:37.860 --> 00:52:39.860
and I was honestly discharged,

00:52:39.860 --> 00:52:41.860
I went to one of the old clubs

00:52:41.860 --> 00:52:43.860
that everybody used to go to.

00:52:43.860 --> 00:52:45.860
And to my surprise,

00:52:45.860 --> 00:52:48.860
one of the guys that I worked with

00:52:48.860 --> 00:52:50.860
and the Air Force was there.

00:52:50.860 --> 00:52:52.860
We got to talking.

00:52:52.860 --> 00:52:54.860
And right there,

00:52:54.860 --> 00:52:58.860
that very night, we devised this plan to go to Thailand.

00:52:58.860 --> 00:53:00.860
And I got some drugs.

00:53:00.860 --> 00:53:02.860
Two months later, that's what we did.

00:53:02.860 --> 00:53:03.860
Just to get there,

00:53:03.860 --> 00:53:05.860
we had to go through a channel

00:53:05.860 --> 00:53:08.860
of waterways through the jungle.

00:53:08.860 --> 00:53:11.860
When we got to this one little island

00:53:11.860 --> 00:53:15.860
where this drug lord was,

00:53:15.860 --> 00:53:16.860
we picked up the drugs.

00:53:16.860 --> 00:53:18.860
And when we got to the airport,

00:53:18.860 --> 00:53:20.860
this Thai colonel

00:53:20.860 --> 00:53:22.860
and the police force,

00:53:22.860 --> 00:53:25.860
he put a 38 right here

00:53:25.860 --> 00:53:26.860
and he told me,

00:53:26.860 --> 00:53:29.860
please do not try to resist me.

00:53:30.860 --> 00:53:31.860
So from there, of course,

00:53:31.860 --> 00:53:33.860
we went to our jail,

00:53:33.860 --> 00:53:34.860
Clung Prim Prison,

00:53:34.860 --> 00:53:36.860
right there in Thailand.

00:53:36.860 --> 00:53:39.860
Life in Clung Prim was pretty grim.

00:53:39.860 --> 00:53:42.860
And so you only got fear twice a day.

00:53:42.860 --> 00:53:44.860
They wouldn't serve it to us.

00:53:44.860 --> 00:53:47.860
They would put it out in the middle of the yard.

00:53:47.860 --> 00:53:51.860
And you had to run for it.

00:53:51.860 --> 00:53:53.860
Awful.

00:53:53.860 --> 00:53:54.860
Two months.

00:53:54.860 --> 00:53:57.860
I lost 130 pounds.

00:53:57.860 --> 00:54:00.860
And so I had to fight.

00:54:00.860 --> 00:54:02.860
It was crazy.

00:54:02.860 --> 00:54:06.860
We had this British gentleman

00:54:06.860 --> 00:54:08.860
come to visit us

00:54:08.860 --> 00:54:10.860
while we were in prison.

00:54:10.860 --> 00:54:12.860
And he told us that

00:54:12.860 --> 00:54:15.860
he was from the American consulate

00:54:15.860 --> 00:54:17.860
and that he wanted to help us.

00:54:17.860 --> 00:54:19.860
And he said, let me tell you something.

00:54:19.860 --> 00:54:20.860
You're in a lot of trouble.

00:54:20.860 --> 00:54:22.860
So as it turned out,

00:54:22.860 --> 00:54:26.860
this man was the chief narcotics agent

00:54:26.860 --> 00:54:29.860
for the whole Southeast Asian area.

00:54:29.860 --> 00:54:31.860
And he said, I want you to work for me

00:54:31.860 --> 00:54:33.860
as a special agent.

00:54:33.860 --> 00:54:36.860
And so I told him, okay, you know, I'll try it.

00:54:36.860 --> 00:54:38.860
And then back to Okinawa.

00:54:38.860 --> 00:54:43.179
And that's where I started to work as an agent.

00:54:43.179 --> 00:54:45.179
He said, you're not going to get paid.

00:54:45.179 --> 00:54:48.179
You know, you're going to have to deal drugs to survive.

00:54:48.179 --> 00:54:50.179
And along the way,

00:54:50.179 --> 00:54:52.179
I set up drug dealers

00:54:52.179 --> 00:54:54.179
who was dealing pretty big.

00:54:54.179 --> 00:54:56.179
After a year of that,

00:54:56.179 --> 00:54:58.179
and they reviewed my case

00:54:58.179 --> 00:55:00.179
and they gave me an opportunity

00:55:00.179 --> 00:55:03.179
to either keep working

00:55:03.179 --> 00:55:05.179
as one of their special agents

00:55:05.179 --> 00:55:07.179
so I got out of the business.

00:55:07.179 --> 00:55:09.179
So I chose to get out of the business.

00:55:09.179 --> 00:55:12.179
I had decided that I had to change my life.

00:55:12.179 --> 00:55:15.179
I was disgusted with the way I was living.

00:55:15.179 --> 00:55:17.179
And so I was sitting in my apartment

00:55:17.179 --> 00:55:19.179
late one afternoon

00:55:19.179 --> 00:55:21.179
and as a little lady, you know,

00:55:21.179 --> 00:55:22.179
knocked on the door,

00:55:22.179 --> 00:55:23.179
a little Japanese lady.

