And I've been going every sense.

00:56:20.179 --> 00:56:23.179
I realized that I had to

00:56:23.179 --> 00:56:26.179
change my lifestyle completely.

00:56:26.179 --> 00:56:28.179
I made rapid changes,

00:56:28.179 --> 00:56:30.179
internal changes.

00:56:30.179 --> 00:56:33.179
My whole thinking process has changed.

00:56:33.179 --> 00:56:37.179
I was baptized on August 30th, 1974.

00:56:37.179 --> 00:56:39.179
They I'll never forget.

00:56:39.179 --> 00:56:43.179
The best thing for me to do was to return home

00:56:43.179 --> 00:56:47.179
and go to the local congregation there

00:56:47.179 --> 00:56:49.179
where there would be, you know,

00:56:49.179 --> 00:56:52.179
literally qualified men to help me

00:56:52.179 --> 00:56:55.179
to continue to grow spiritually.

00:56:55.179 --> 00:56:58.179
I really, really wanted to go to Bethel

00:56:58.179 --> 00:57:01.179
and so I determined that that's

00:57:01.179 --> 00:57:03.179
what I was going to do.

00:57:03.179 --> 00:57:05.179
And so I made it a goal

00:57:05.179 --> 00:57:07.179
and I stuck with it, you know,

00:57:07.179 --> 00:57:10.179
for five years after I got home.

00:57:10.179 --> 00:57:14.179
And finally, I got the privilege.

00:57:14.179 --> 00:57:17.179
The privilege that was extended to me

00:57:17.179 --> 00:57:20.179
of coming to serve at Bethel

00:57:20.179 --> 00:57:23.179
has stretched out to be 35 years

00:57:23.179 --> 00:57:25.179
and I can't believe it.

00:57:25.179 --> 00:57:27.179
Since serving here at Bethel,

00:57:27.179 --> 00:57:30.179
I've served in a number of assignments.

00:57:30.179 --> 00:57:35.179
Currently, I serve as a desk receptionist,

00:57:35.179 --> 00:57:39.179
caring for building maintenance duties,

00:57:39.179 --> 00:57:41.179
the occupants of the building,

00:57:41.179 --> 00:57:43.179
greeting guests,

00:57:43.179 --> 00:57:45.179
and just generally trying to be

00:57:45.179 --> 00:57:48.179
as helpful as possible.

00:57:48.179 --> 00:57:51.179
I mean, I think about all the good things

00:57:51.179 --> 00:57:55.179
that Jehovah has done for me

00:57:55.179 --> 00:57:57.179
and for my wife, Bonnie.

00:57:57.179 --> 00:57:59.179
It's been phenomenal.

00:57:59.179 --> 00:58:02.179
I've learned that you can't really do anything

00:58:02.179 --> 00:58:04.179
in your own strength.

00:58:04.179 --> 00:58:07.179
Jehovah, he searches the heart.

00:58:07.179 --> 00:58:10.179
He looks for people who are yearning

00:58:10.179 --> 00:58:12.179
for something better, the direction,

00:58:12.179 --> 00:58:13.179
but only he can give.

00:58:13.179 --> 00:58:17.179
Because I shudder at the course I could have taken

00:58:17.179 --> 00:58:21.179
on a number of occasions that would have led to,

00:58:21.179 --> 00:58:23.179
you know, a different outcome.

00:58:23.179 --> 00:58:25.179
And so I'm very happy to be in the truth.

00:58:25.179 --> 00:58:29.179
It is absolutely on the best way of life.

00:58:29.179 --> 00:58:31.179
I don't know much,

00:58:31.179 --> 00:58:33.179
but I do know this.

00:58:33.179 --> 00:58:36.179
That Jehovah is real.

00:58:36.179 --> 00:58:40.179
He's very kind and merciful.

00:58:40.179 --> 00:58:44.670
I do know that.

00:58:44.670 --> 00:58:46.670
It was a delightful experience.

00:58:46.670 --> 00:58:49.670
Many of our viewers can relate to that experience

00:58:49.670 --> 00:58:51.670
and have come to appreciate a warm

00:58:51.670 --> 00:58:54.670
and abiding relationship with Jehovah.

00:58:54.670 --> 00:58:58.670
And even if we have been taught the truth from infancy,

00:58:58.670 --> 00:59:00.670
