00:59:03.670 --> 00:59:05.670
This moves us to share the good news

00:59:05.670 --> 00:59:07.670
of the kingdom with people regardless

00:59:07.670 --> 00:59:09.670
of their background or status.

00:59:09.670 --> 00:59:11.670
I couldn't agree more.

